{"tid":2221363,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"哥迪奧拿：曼城要輸番場","createTime":"2020-09-28T10:04:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T10:22:28.000Z","uid":21255,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"92e0ed86fb1eaaa7dea343b47ac7155b6843d6de","tid":2221363,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T10:04:19.000Z","msg":"「你有否看過贏4:0之後球員會覺得累?我從沒見過，當贏波時你會覺得更加舒服，士氣亦會提高。我們需要贏出比賽搶分，但我更希望可以輸一場‥&hellip;當然只是說笑，但這樣的確可減壓力。」<br />\n<br />\n「最近我聽到很多對不同領隊的批評，但這並不公平，現在只踢了5場聯賽，如果我的球隊輸波，我一定是最清楚原因的一個。」<br />\n<br />\n哥帥認為要贏出所有比賽是沒可能，要永遠保持最佳狀態都沒可能，其他領隊正面對這個問題，所以自己已有心理準備。<br />\n<br />\n對於現在的成績，哥帥坦言十分滿意：「我從沒想過可以到這種程度，因為我是新領隊，不過現在只是9月，要作定論仍然過早。」（<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=Wx0cKZaQlto0GELw8F4hIWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=a86336ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>）"},{"pid":"3556b0ee722ac6f41b8d8365b40f6ad022887c77","tid":2221363,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T10:05:03.000Z","msg":"回"},{"pid":"34551f76ab0b50f1da08499cc98ee0be67caa77c","tid":2221363,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3556b0ee722ac6f41b8d8365b40f6ad022887c77","tid":2221363,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T10:05:03.000Z","msg":"回"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T10:05:55.000Z","msg":"到"},{"pid":"a7482337769e8b4e22aa3b17ead44b85b3936e54","tid":2221363,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34551f76ab0b50f1da08499cc98ee0be67caa77c","tid":2221363,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3556b0ee722ac6f41b8d8365b40f6ad022887c77","tid":2221363,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T10:05:03.000Z","msg":"回"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T10:05:55.000Z","msg":"到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T10:14:24.000Z","msg":"錯"},{"pid":"bd081c4293a5fa7b1b1c01f7f625fb5276ec2742","tid":2221363,"uid":21255,"like":0,"disli